# Frontend Architecture

- Build reusable, composable UI components with clear props contracts.
- Keep business logic out of presentation components.
- Use hooks/services/selectors for stateful or derived logic.
- Keep state predictable; avoid ad hoc global mutable state.
- Centralize API calls in dedicated clients/services.
- Handle loading, error, and empty states consistently.
